{"tid":1778012,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【抗暴之戰】《孤星淚》社區音樂會登陸大埔 600市民參與","createTime":"2019-12-10T15:16:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T15:17:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3d9540a13370ab846f80e452dbbcb6567737dc44","tid":1778012,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T15:16:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191210/60364258\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191210%2F60364258&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwgg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=c5fd046e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191210%2F60364258&h=3025975d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191210/60364258</a><br />\n<br />\n【抗暴之戰】《孤星淚》社區音樂會登陸大埔 600市民參與<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191210/large/1575983572_2f9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191210%2Flarge%2F1575983572_2f9e.jpg&h=c3608c3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一群關心社會的音樂人於今年10月開始在社區巡迴表演《孤星淚》，主辦單位今晚8點半於大埔海濱公園露天劇場再辦音樂會。晚上有約600名市民到場欣賞，現場氣氛良好，同場有特別嘉賓龍門冰室老闆阿傑，與市民分享心聲。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【蘋聞追Click】《蘋果》中大驗出催淚彈殘留 泥土殘留達致敏水平<br />\n<br />\n《孤星淚(Les Miserable)》音樂會發起人張先生表示，表演目的是為香港人加油打氣，今日已是第4區表演，劇團有約40名義工參與，表演約一小時，唱12首歌。《孤星淚》戶外音樂會於10月28日首度在觀海濱公園演出，其後到過荔枝角等地方。該音樂會受市民歡迎，發起人曾於網上招募義工參與。<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n【匿名港警爆大鑊】<br />\n韓國KBS時事節目《時事直擊：香港 被自殺》<br />\n一按即睇<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n【撐學生】<br />\n召集有心人 撐學生全年睇《蘋果》<br />\n立即按此<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n你敢爆，我敢獎！ 立即WhatsApp《蘋果》24小時爆相爆片熱線 或致電：63836568 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191210/large/1575983572_8456.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191210%2Flarge%2F1575983572_8456.jpg&h=a1b385fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網民晚上8時在大埔海濱公園露天劇場發起孤星淚音樂演奏會。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191210/large/1575983572_c5c6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191210%2Flarge%2F1575983572_c5c6.jpg&h=14a68c59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大批街坊到場聆聽。馬耀文攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191210/large/1575983574_9d28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191210%2Flarge%2F1575983574_9d28.jpg&h=08277c55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n街坊幾乎坐滿整個露天劇場。馬耀文攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191210/large/1575983575_4f9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191210%2Flarge%2F1575983575_4f9e.jpg&h=56a64020&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有管弦樂隊現場演奏。馬耀文攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191210/large/1575983574_82b4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191210%2Flarge%2F1575983574_82b4.jpg&h=585e01a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n藝人阮民安現身支持。馬耀文攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191210/large/1575984355_58d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191210%2Flarge%2F1575984355_58d5.jpg&h=d8a394d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n特別嘉賓龍門冰室老闆阿傑，與市民分享心聲。馬耀文攝<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n上水清潔工中磚不治 警懸紅80萬緝兇<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n【短片】松柏新邨單位遭爆竊 失約30萬手錶"},{"pid":"01b3edabe6ff561465afc1756b16f94e0a3b300c","tid":1778012,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T15:17:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}